{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.640", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.840", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.200", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von Jean Sibelius, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "14.800", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dem ber\u00fchmten finnischen Komponisten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "14.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.440", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stammt das Bonmot: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.280", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201e\u00dcber Musik kann man am besten mit Bankdirektoren reden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "25.960", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "K\u00fcnstler redeten ja nur \u00fcbers Geld.\u201c Zumindest die erste Behauptung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "25.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.120", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Kunstsinn der Kassenh\u00fcter betreffend, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.320", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deckt sich auch mit meinen pers\u00f6nlichen Erfahrungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.520", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nicht nur mit Bankdirektoren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.520", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch mit Haushalts- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Finanzpolitikern kann man ganz hervorragend \u00fcber Kultur reden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.200", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das macht sich dann in Euro und Cent bezahlt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wiederum K\u00fcnstler und Kreative wie auch Kulturpolitiker freut."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.600", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin jedenfalls sehr zufrieden mit dem Ausgang der Gespr\u00e4che zum Kultur- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.200", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Medienhaushalt\u00a02018; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.760", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn erneut konnte die Kulturfinanzierung des Bundes signifikant gesteigert werden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.800", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Wohle zahlreicher kultureller Einrichtungen und Projekte im ganzen Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.760", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Lassen Sie mich ganz kurz auf die wesentlichen Ver\u00e4nderungen eingehen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.960", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie bereits im M\u00e4rz in der Generaldebatte hier im Deutschen Bundestag angek\u00fcndigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.560", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist es mein Ziel, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.560", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in dieser Legislaturperiode die Aufarbeitung von und den Umgang mit Best\u00e4nden aus kolonialen Kontexten in Sammlungen und Museen voranzubringen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.080", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb stocke ich mit meinem Haushalt\u00a02018 die Mittel f\u00fcr Provenienzforschung ein weiteres Mal auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.120", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um mehr als eine halbe Million Euro gegen\u00fcber dem ersten Regierungsentwurf. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.840", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "F\u00fcr den Regierungsentwurf\u00a02019, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.440", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir derzeit erarbeiten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "beabsichtige ich gerade in diesem Bereich weitere Erh\u00f6hungen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.760", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein erster wichtiger Schritt war die Unterst\u00fctzung des Deutschen Museumsbundes bei der Erarbeitung eines Leitfadens zum Umgang mit Sammlungsgut aus kolonialen Kontexten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.040", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Den haben wir am Montag ver\u00f6ffentlicht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich bin sicher: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.920", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er wird sowohl den Museen als auch der Politik helfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.880", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "diesem anspruchsvollen und\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.280", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das lernt man, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.840", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man sich damit befasst\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.360", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sehr vielschichtigen Thema gerecht zu werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.320", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Aufgabe sollten und, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.880", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir uns mit Aufrichtigkeit und Nachdruck stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viel zu lange war die Kolonialzeit ein blinder Fleck in unserer Erinnerungskultur; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.720", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und viel zu lange war das in dieser Zeit geschehene Unrecht vergessen und verdr\u00e4ngt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.120", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es endlich ans Licht zu holen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.240", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist Teil der historischen Verantwortung Deutschlands gegen\u00fcber den ehemaligen Kolonien und Voraussetzung f\u00fcr Vers\u00f6hnung und Verst\u00e4ndigung mit den dort lebenden Menschen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist es gut, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "177.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Fragen auch mit dem Baufortschritt beim Humboldt Forum ins Zentrum der \u00f6ffentlichen Aufmerksamkeit ger\u00fcckt sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "177.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "180.880", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort haben wir gestern einstimmig\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "180.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Jongen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.640", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit allen in den Stiftungsrat entsandten Vertretern aus Parteien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.920", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Regierung und Experten Hartmut \u00adDorgerloh zum Generalintendanten gew\u00e4hlt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.600", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dass wir diesen gro\u00dfen und, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.320", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wichtigen Schritt in dieser Einm\u00fctigkeit getan haben\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.760", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das war nicht unbedingt zu erwarten; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.280", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "freut mich aber umso mehr\u00a0\u2013,"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.120", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zeigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wirksam eine Kultur der Verst\u00e4ndigung sein kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.120", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hartmut Dorgerloh wird diese\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.200", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so beschreibt er selbst das Humboldt\u00a0Forum\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.000", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u201eFreist\u00e4tte f\u00fcr Kunst und Wissenschaft\u201c der Allgemeinheit erschlie\u00dfen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.760", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich danke an dieser Stelle ausdr\u00fccklich Neil \u00adMacGregor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der bislang gemeinsam mit Horst Bredekamp und Hermann Parzinger den inhaltlichen Feinschliff am Gro\u00dfprojekt Humboldt\u00a0Forum vorgenommen hat. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.880", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist damit gut ger\u00fcstet f\u00fcr die letzten Monate bis zur Er\u00f6ffnung Ende\u00a02019. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.440", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte an dieser Stelle auch ausdr\u00fccklich Herrn Staatssekret\u00e4r Pronold danken\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.760", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "er ist leider gerade gegangen\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.680", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der das Projekt bisher vonseiten des Bundesbauministeriums ganz hervorragend gemanagt hat."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "253.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Humboldt Forum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "253.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.080", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dieser \u201eFreist\u00e4tte\u201c, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.440", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "laden wir Besucher ein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.920", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Weltb\u00fcrger zu sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "260.760", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie wichtig es wieder geworden ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "260.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "263.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "demokratische Errungenschaften wie Kunstfreiheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "263.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Pressefreiheit und Meinungsfreiheit aktiv zu verteidigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.600", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "m\u00fcssen wir t\u00e4glich\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "269.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.200", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00fcbrigens nicht nur mit Blick auf manche Nachbarl\u00e4nder\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.120", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erleben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.840", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Immerhin darf Hajo Seppelt jetzt doch nach Russland einreisen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.160", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber wenn wir auf den dortigen Theatermacher Serebrennikow schauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "281.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "284.200", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der nicht zum Theatertreffen kommen konnte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "284.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.120", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "288.920", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie schwer es unabh\u00e4ngige Journalisten in Ungarn haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "288.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "295.400", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und wenn wir die zunehmende Einschr\u00e4nkung der Medienfreiheit in Polen durch das neue Mediengesetz beobachten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "295.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "297.920", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir mit ansehen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "297.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "299.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Liu Xia, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "299.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "302.160", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Witwe des Schriftstellers Liu Xiaobo, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "302.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "303.720", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in China leiden muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "303.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "305.480", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder wenn wir sehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "305.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "310.720", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
